Based on Potrero de los Funes Circuit near San Juan, Argentina
The circuit is semi-permanent, created by modifying the ring road
that encircles Lake Potrero de los Funes, at the course's center.

Length: 6.270 km (3.896mi)
Width: 14m
Year of construction: 1987/2008

